The initial release of this management information module.

usdDs1Agent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdDs1Agent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the DS1 component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdDs1AgentV1.name: usdDs1AgentV1
usdDs1AgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the DS1 component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the DS1 component was supported in the Unisphere
        RX 1.0 system releases.
usdDs1AgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. This version became obsolete when new objects were added to the Unisphere-Data-DS1-MIB.

usdDs1AgentV2.name: usdDs1AgentV2
usdDs1AgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the DS1 component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the DS1 component was supported in the Unisphere
        RX 1.1 thru RX 2.x system releases.
usdDs1AgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. This version became obsolete when dynamic DS1 interface support was added to the Unisphere-Data-DS1-MIB.

usdDs1AgentV3.name: usdDs1AgentV3
usdDs1AgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the DS1 component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the DS1 component was supported in the Unisphere
        RX 3.x system releases.
usdDs1AgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. This version became obsolete when far end statistics support was added and more configuration objects were added to the Unisphere-Data-DS1-MIB.

usdDs1AgentV4.name: usdDs1AgentV4
usdDs1AgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the DS1 component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the DS1 component is supported in the Unisphere
        RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdDs1AgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
